1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with the problem of artist style transfer on real world photographs, which is a common problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses neural networks and deep learning techniques to achieve artist style transfer, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses adversarial training and quadratic potential divergence for stable learning process, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating stylized images, which is a common problem in computer graphics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with transferring the style of an artist onto a photograph, which is a common problem in multimedia applications.
